<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bitcoins are fungible simply because it is sta=
ndard convention among Bitcoin users to=C2=A0<em>treat=C2=A0</em>them as fu=
ngible, but they <em>are=C2=A0</em>distinguishable from one another, and if=
=C2=A0you wanted to discriminate among Bitcoins you=C2=A0<em>could</em>. Pe=
ople mostly don=E2=80=99t, but the last thing on that list =E2=80=94=C2=A0=
=E2=80=9Ctry not to accept=C2=A0Bitcoins that have been stolen or are <a hr=
